{"tid":1692860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前c朗髮型師被捅死在酒店","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:53:14.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"427d4f1d150b49c012e1c84754469ccc3bd97e48","tid":1692860,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GL5kZeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGL5kZeo.png&h=6516f9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《都靈體育報》報導，一位名叫的Ricardo Marques Ferreira的髮型師今天被發現被捅死在蘇黎世的一家酒店裡，他是C羅等多位名人的理髮師。<br />\n<br />\n 當地媒體稱，已有一位39歲的巴西男子被捕。 而酒店房間裡遍地是血，還瀰漫著酒精味。<br />\n<br />\n 2015年，當C羅還在為皇馬效力時，他為拍照前C羅的形像做過最後修容。"},{"pid":"03cba852a53c770f2a1ec9a7a3f13db7a95f600d","tid":1692860,"uid":47023,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯還瀰漫著精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd9affda3779f07c517e4088019e30430d1590d","tid":1692860,"uid":243526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"C朗人都敢殺"},{"pid":"76de15203e38539d8238140daa7924207282184f","tid":1692860,"uid":209773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"剪柒咗人個頭俾人殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46b6cd16442cd7c527efa2802a73e8206ef4b76","tid":1692860,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"用鉛筆捅？"},{"pid":"aa01f533f26722c2094a9a510841002404e7aca6","tid":1692860,"uid":53855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"侏儒妒忌c朗太型<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人隊林c朗前造型師發泄<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1d5db10a415f92aeba51bd25b25a8e16c701bf","tid":1692860,"uid":7621